{"tid":1121140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女消防員與主管辦公室做愛　遭同袍偷拍要脅就範","createTime":"2019-04-23T06:44:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T09:56:43.000Z","uid":244704,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9db3f96f1cbc6c95f43c4375dd1d9a4a10283821","tid":1121140,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T06:44:44.000Z","msg":"台灣新北市一名女消防員，今年2月在分局的主管室內，與男主管發生性行為，被另一名男隊員偷拍，事後該女隊員更遭偷拍者以公開影片要脅性交。女隊員因情緒不穩，需入院治療。<br />\n<br />\n新北市消防局表示，本月10日得悉事件後，立即由督察室及轄區大隊主管約談當事人，其中同樣未婚的男主管與女隊員，坦承曾在主管室內做出不當行為，兩人分別被給予記過2次及1次的處分，另男方被調任非主管職位。女方則因情緒不穩正住院，未來將接受輔導，視身心復原情況再作處理。<br />\n<br />\n至於事件中偷拍的男子，遭消防局約談時否認有偷拍行為。由於兩名當事人未提出起訴，消防局也無法細究，而該男子於本月中旬退伍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190423/bkn-20190423011755136-0423_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190423%2Fbkn-20190423011755136-0423_00952_001.html&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9ODyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=68bd5c22\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190423/bkn-20190423011755136-0423_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3abd4706380d9bcffe3e0cffe602e56c37e0c28d","tid":1121140,"uid":51620,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又新北市 其實呢個地方出左咩事"},{"pid":"77bf84da5b75227a93d3f5c8a5a0ac0695f8da9d","tid":1121140,"uid":52023,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n成本H漫劇情出哂嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5874f48af0d5345f6b2fe8e36d73fa908298577","tid":1121140,"uid":38904,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://66.media.